---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Work On Yourself — Soul Care Intensive for Christian Leaders & Pastors"
	description="Work On Yourself is a twelve-month Soul Care Intensive for Christian leaders, pastors, and ministers whose outer success has outpaced their inner life. Restoration starts here."
	ogImage="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/pmowd8uo/production/981bdb635a6b15b39fa91fb9a3fbc6b3dc4f5707-1200x630?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format.jpg"
>
	<Fragment slot="head">
		<meta name="keywords" content="Work On Yourself, soul care for leaders, Christian leadership restoration, pastor burnout, spiritual formation leaders, inner healing Christian leaders, Christian executive coaching, soul care intensive, ministry burnout recovery, Spirit Media Publishing" />
		<meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
		<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "Service",
			"name": "Work On Yourself — Soul Care Intensive",
			"provider": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Spirit Media Publishing", "url": "https://spiritmediapublishing.com" },
			"serviceType": "Christian Leadership Coaching",
			"description": "A twelve-month Soul Care Intensive for Christian leaders, pastors, and ministers whose outer success has outpaced their inner life.",
			"url": "https://spiritmediapublishing.com/work-on-yourself"
		})}</script>
	</Fragment>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-stone-50 px-6 py-12 lg:py-20 lg:py-28 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="hero-stagger">
						<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-4">Work On Yourself</p>
						<h1 class="type-hero">A Soul Care Intensive<br /><span class="text-red">for Leaders</span></h1>
						<p class="mt-6 type-body-lg max-w-xl">Whose outer success has outpaced their inner life.</p>
						<div class="mt-8">
							<a href="https://workonyourself.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-md bg-red px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-red-deep">Visit WorkOnYourself.com →</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="hidden lg:grid grid-cols-3 gap-3" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="zoom-in">
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-deep aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-soft aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-deep aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-muted aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-soft aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-deep aspect-square"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE CHALLENGE -->
		<section class="bg-stone-100 py-12 lg:py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
				<div>
					<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">The Challenge</p>
					<h2 class="type-section-heading mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">When Success Outpaces the Soul</h2>
					<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">You built the business. You carry the influence. You've been rewarded for your capacity to think, decide, and deliver. But somewhere along the way, the soul went untended.</p>
					<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="3">Stress became normal. Margin disappeared. Faith endured without intimacy. You are physically present but emotionally numb. Highly successful — yet lacking any genuine sense of significance.</p>
					<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="4">When leaders like you seek help, they encounter a fragmented landscape: therapy disconnected from faith, coaching focused on performance, retreats without long-term integration. No one integrates the full journey within a single pastorally stewarded container.</p>
				</div>
				<div data-animate="fade-in" data-delay="2">
					<img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/pmowd8uo/production/5432c9da4368625822d9697301955f3bb2df9245-4096x2160?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format.jpg" alt="Prayer and soul care" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg object-cover" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE SOLUTION -->
		<section class="bg-stone-50 py-12 lg:py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">The Solution</p>
				<h2 class="type-section-heading mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Until Now.</h2>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">Work On Yourself is a twelve-month Soul Care Intensive — pastorally stewarded, relationally grounded, and theologically centered on restoration to God as Father. This is not therapy, coaching, or a retreat. It is a protected season where leaders are accompanied rather than optimized, stewarded rather than evaluated.</p>
				<blockquote class="bg-ink-soft text-white rounded-2xl p-8 my-8" data-animate="fade-in" data-delay="3">
					<p class="font-serif text-xl italic leading-relaxed">"And what do you benefit if you gain the whole world but lose your own soul?"</p>
					<cite class="block mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-red-soft not-italic">— Mark 8:36 (FHB)</cite>
				</blockquote>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="4">Stewarded by Kevin and Shelly White.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="bg-red px-6 py-12 lg:py-20 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl mb-4" data-animate="fade-up">Ready to Begin the Journey?</h2>
				<p class="text-stone-200 type-body-lg mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Work On Yourself is for leaders ready to prioritize their inner life with the same intentionality they bring to their outer one.</p>
				<a href="https://workonyourself.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-stone-50 text-red font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-md hover:bg-red-wash transition-colors" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">WorkOnYourself.com →</a>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
